    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/school-absenteeism-truancy-education-students">
                                    Skipping School: America’s Hidden Education Crisis
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Absenteeism has nearly doubled since the pandemic. With state and federal governments largely abdicating any role in getting kids back into classrooms, some schools have turned to private companies for a reimagined version of the truant officer.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/alec-macgillis">Alec MacGillis</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-01-08EST06:00">Jan. 8, 6 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
