    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/state-of-disrepair">State of Disrepair</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/idaho-students-educators-show-us-effects-of-underfunded-schools">
                                    Falling Apart
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Students and educators in Idaho show us what it’s like when a state fails to fund school repairs.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/asia-fields">Asia Fields</a>, ProPublica, and <span class="name">Becca Savransky</span>, <a href="https://www.idahostatesman.com/">Idaho Statesman</a>, illustrations by <span class="name">Pia Guerra</span> for <a href="https://www.propublica.org">ProPublica</a>, design by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/anna-donlan">Anna Donlan</a>, ProPublica,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-12-15EST05:00">Dec. 15, 2023, 5 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

                <p class="story-card__unit">Local Reporting Network</p>
            </div>
